    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/04f9deffe21f4fd67bb42ec6ce326896.poster.avif?t=1771332566\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/04f9deffe21f4fd67bb42ec6ce326896.webm?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/04f9deffe21f4fd67bb42ec6ce326896.mp4?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃跑</h2>在这款 Rogue-lite 地牢爬行游戏中，扮演被锁在地下塔中的古代奇美拉。从古老的监狱中爬出来，穿过充满强大生物的楼层。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/953a0fddf05f30bcc54f5f47c2a1f87a.poster.avif?t=1771332566\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/953a0fddf05f30bcc54f5f47c2a1f87a.webm?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/953a0fddf05f30bcc54f5f47c2a1f87a.mp4?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以你的方式获得权力</h2>通过嫁接敌人的肢体来使用独特的能力，从他们那里夺取力量。使用饰品打造各种造型，成为一股不可阻挡的力量。从商店解锁文物，改变你的游戏风格。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找真相</h2>揭开塔中的秘密，找出你被监禁的真正原因。寻找一位神秘的盟友来帮助你穿越这个危险的世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/78791e0189b5891ead2155a044ae2a55.poster.avif?t=1771332566\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/78791e0189b5891ead2155a044ae2a55.webm?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069320/extras/78791e0189b5891ead2155a044ae2a55.mp4?t=1771332566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >杀出一条血路</h2>穿过塔楼的三个不同楼层，每个角落都充满了危险和危险。每层楼都讲述了塔楼的不同故事供您揭开。<br><br>你能逃脱吗？",
